0Z","msg":"10. 官塘區<br />\n<br />\n高雷近年並非獨大，地利亞不斷引入南亞人, 朱石麟亦開始要老師做沙包俾老師練功，望提昇實力 , 例如試下古惑仔漫畫咁，用拳頭睇下打唔打到個老師飛起(當然飛唔起.所以繼續練)。迦南開始有進步, 普照,利瑪竇,瑪利諾開始力弱。何南金近年俾差佬強力打壓，已經冇乜理江湖事，專注係校內過淫蕩生活。係入面想需求其TAKE件女入廁所就得,冇CONDOM 問下FRIEND就一定有"},{"pid":"2f2a509ff3a30519d98021f98645f6f901409d2b","tid":736404,"uid":171124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"換左校長好耐<br />\n依家都算唔錯 其實<br />\n無哂打交"},{"pid":"7b862ee45e1b94188e77752ebf9c64c8ee6ea9a6","tid":736404,"uid":27970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:58:10.000Z","msg":"聽講，好多卧底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2a82da622830db9cb669b4cecdd85c7ac09193","tid":736404,"uid":90630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"打贏入差館 打輸入醫院<br />\n高雷校訓"},{"pid":"8ad8d174eab58f1faacedc699451dc4bce3156b3","tid":736404,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b2a82da622830db9cb669b4cecdd85c7ac09193","tid":736404,"uid":90630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"打贏入差館 打輸入醫院<br />\n高雷校訓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"真真正正嘅往左走往右走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5547a2eedf3e9298bdf15067418b9be4d2c41cd5","tid":736404,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"格鬥中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b027bd2e7a298c57b87d473992a3a26ec0d27d","tid":736404,"uid":170383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:59:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}